            "value": "The image in my head of the ideal man has always been tall, athletic, confident, cool, dominant, and more often than not White. I think I‚Äôve always subconsciously avoided those types ‚Äî¬†I don‚Äôt have any friends like that. I‚Äôm not sure why. I just get nervous. I forget how to act. I feign coolness. I shed my entire personality for a more relaxed tone. I start to call people around me ‚Äúman‚Äù."
