          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "I appreciated the example. It taught me that I need not listen to the voices saying Asian male bodies were not attractive. The film probably did make many of its other viewers question why they held, expected, or were satisfied by particular media archetypes of Asian people in the first place. But did I have to look and act like Colin Khoo to love my body?"
          },
