            "type": "text",
            "value": "Nevertheless, Asian-American men who are strong both physically and emotionally always stand out to me in films and TV. In the show <i>Insecure</i>, the Asian man‚Äôs body has never been involved in some sexless joke. He is strong, he is not intimidated in his relationships, he is not afraid to say what he wants. He has sex scenes ü§Ø that are not part of a joke ü§Ø and are sexual and explicit ü§Ø."
